{"tid":971694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬英九搬出《中華民國憲法》要蔡英文承認九二共識","createTime":"2019-01-06T23:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T01:47:56.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b25496d3a2e8cce4404c98a14dbee26bfb0273d3","tid":971694,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:35:11.000Z","msg":"馬搬出《憲法》要蔡承認九二共識<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：2019/01/07 05:00<br />\n<br />\n總統蔡英文上任後不接受九二共識，前天更呼籲各政黨不要再提九二共識，前總統馬英九昨在臉書強力反擊，我方的「一中各表」就是「一個中華民國，兩個地區─台灣地區與大陸地區」的《憲法》定位，不會表到「兩個中國、一中一台、或台灣獨立」，因為這是《中華民國憲法》所不允許的，他在2015年「馬習會」正式會議中特別和中國國家主席習近平強調過，當時還有會議紀錄的逐字稿。<br />\n<br />\n馬英九質疑，蔡英文拒絕九二共識，卻又說「我們不反對兩岸互動，我們也願意坐下來談」，但兩年多來，兩岸有什麼互動？談過些什麼？蔡不接受九二共識，怎麼能期待大陸當局跟她互動呢？面對兩岸情勢益加險峻，雙方應誠心回歸「原汁原味」的九二共識，台灣不要否定九二共識，大陸也不要無謂攻擊一中各表，蔡拒絕九二共識，無法解決兩岸問題，美國、日本也都幫不上忙。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20190107/38225973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20190107%2F38225973&d=cf7i4YNeRLUuLoCXodI%2Bhsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5a2b57b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20190107%2F38225973&h=466a63f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20190107/38225973</a>"},{"pid":"16e32e7bb90d694ae1d1555b3872adbc6499c573","tid":971694,"uid":36533,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:37:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a701c8b44f2575b14c82ba79f1930aac34818f0","tid":971694,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:38:26.000Z","msg":"我係總統我話得就得啦"},{"pid":"a5e89bf0a22fe9a8a686f773ecbd9f74fc789652","tid":971694,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:40:22.000Z","msg":"馬暗示要修憲"},{"pid":"a7933e4012e38e3f4dcf4e9d01a42c13afd1f808","tid":971694,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:46:58.000Z","msg":"前總統馬英九昨在臉書強力反擊，我方的「一中各表」就是「一個中華民國，兩個地區─<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣地區與大陸地區」的《憲法》定位</span>，不會表到「兩個中國、一中一台、或台灣獨立」，因為這是《中華民國憲法》所不允許的。<br />\n<br />\n憲法中搵唔到&quot;九二共識&quot;或&quot;一中各表&quot;字眼"},{"pid":"a7799011491195bade5a332dbc6cdb469afac8a4","tid":971694,"uid":36901,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:48:28.000Z","msg":"咁快打倒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬英九史丹佛演講 頭銜用「中華民國(台灣)前總統」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://udn.com/news/amp/story/6656/3082745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3082745&d=cf7i4YNeRLUuLoCXodI%2Bhsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fc9ecabc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://udn.com/news/amp/story/6656/3082745</a>"},{"pid":"000c1e68d172bc5507ad8bebcd9a81dc68de4d0d","tid":971694,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:56:14.000Z","msg":"現中華民國憲法係源於國民黨1927年推翻北京中華民國政府後創立<br />\n所以解釋權在kmt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd87c7260ab36353d2bf52db6bf22ed2231f9e6e","tid":971694,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7799011491195bade5a332dbc6cdb469afac8a4","tid":971694,"uid":36901,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T23:48:28.000Z","msg":"咁快打倒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬英九史丹佛演講 頭銜用「中華民國(台灣)前總統」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://udn.com/news/amp/story/6656/3082745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3082745&d=cf7i4YNeRLUuLoCXodI%2Bhsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fc9ecabc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://udn.com/news/amp/story/6656/3082745</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:06:58.000Z","msg":"賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c5555b52667807e7579bd73e73a6d1fe29a220","tid":971694,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quo